OL,4,CWaterstones to encourage shoppers to
OL,5,Cwear masks in stores
OL,6, Waterstones says it will encourage its
OL,7, customers to continue wearing face
OL,8, coverings in its stores after they
OL,9, cease to be compulsory after July 19.
OL,11,FIt is one of the first major chains to
OL,12,Fstate a firm policy on mask wearing.
OL,14,FBusinesses are weighing up what
OL,15,Fapproach to take once Covid measures
OL,16,Fbecome a matter for them to decide.
OL,18,FSome shop workers and staff are worried
OL,19,Fthat abandoning masks will put their
OL,20,Fhealth at risk, but others have reacted
OL,21,Fwith anger at Waterstones' move.
